{# B1 — Page d'erreur : token invalide, expiré ou déjà consommé. #}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lien invalide — MABB Manager</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #063a55 0%, #0b4fa3 60%, #1c88b6 100%);
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        }
        .info-card {
            background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 44px 40px; text-align: center;
            width: 100%; max-width: 440px; box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
        }
        .icon-circle {
            width: 80px; height: 80px; border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #d97706); color: #fff;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2.4rem; margin: 0 auto 18px;
        }
        h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0b1f3a; margin-bottom: 14px; }
        p { color: #475569; line-height: 1.6; font-size: .92rem; margin-bottom: 22px; }
        .btn-retry {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1d4ed8, #2563eb); color: #fff;
            padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 10px; text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700; font-size: .92rem; display: inline-block;
        }
        .btn-retry:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); color: #fff; }
        .back-link { display: block; text-align: center; margin-top: 16px; color: #64748b; text-decoration: none; font-size: .85rem; }
        .back-link:hover { color: #1d4ed8; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="info-card">
        <div class="icon-circle"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle"></i></div>
        <h1>Lien invalide ou expiré</h1>
        <p>
            Ce lien de réinitialisation n'est plus valide. Il a peut-être expiré (validité 1 heure),
            été déjà utilisé, ou il est incorrect.
        </p>
        <a href="{{ path('manager_reset_password_request') }}" class="btn-retry">
            <i class="bi bi-arrow-clockwise"></i> Refaire une demande
        </a>
        <a href="{{ path('manager_login') }}" class="back-link">Retour à la connexion</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
